Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.88,0:53:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,lungo la strada serve Dio.\N>> Va bene. Grazie. Può?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.44,0:54:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Uhuh.\N>> Sì.
